<Folder>
  <name>J1 — Bienvenue a Dublin</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Temple Bar</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Quartier emblematique aux facades colorees. Ambiance musicale, pubs traditionnels. Plus sympa pour une balade photo en journee qu'en soiree avec enfants.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.lovetemplebar.com/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186605-d188821-Reviews-Temple_Bar-Dublin_County_Dublin.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/dublin/temple-bar">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Temple+Bar+Dublin+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day1</styleUrl>
    <address>Temple Bar, Dublin, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>St Stephen&#x27;s Green</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Parc victorien avec lac, canards et aire de jeux. Pause parfaite apres le voyage. Aire de jeux avec toboggan a la cathedrale St Patrick juste a cote.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186605-d189054-Reviews-St_Stephens_Green-Dublin_County_Dublin.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=St+Stephen's+Green+Dublin+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day1</styleUrl>
    <address>St Stephen's Green, Dublin, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J1</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day1</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-6.2499,53.4264,0 -6.2628,53.3456,0 -6.2592,53.3381,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Dublin centre</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-6.2592,53.3381,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J2 — Cap a l&#x27;Ouest — Galway !</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Sean&#x27;s Bar, Athlone</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Plus vieux pub d'Irlande (900 ap. J.-C. !). Dejeuner au bord du Shannon, murs en torchis d'epoque.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.seansbar.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g212091-d1580894-Reviews-Sean_s_Bar-Athlone_County_Westmeath.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sean's+Bar+Athlone+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day2</styleUrl>
    <address>Sean's Bar, Athlone, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Burgess Park</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Parc au bord du Shannon avec aire de jeux. Les enfants se degourdissent apres la route.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Burgess+Park+Athlone+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day2</styleUrl>
    <address>Burgess Park, Athlone, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Galway Latin Quarter &amp; Shop Street</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Coeur vibrant : musiciens de rue, facades colorees, boutiques. Spanish Arch et Long Walk.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186609-d4909613-Reviews-Galway_s_Latin_Quarter-Galway_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/comte-de-galway/galway-gaillimh">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Galway+Latin+Quarter+%26+Shop+Street+Galway+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day2</styleUrl>
    <address>Latin Quarter, Galway, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J2</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day2</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-6.2603,53.3498,0 -7.9408,53.4232,0 -7.938,53.425,0 -9.053,53.2719,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Galway (1ere nuit)</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-9.053,53.2719,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J3 — Burren &amp; Falaises de Moher</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Caherconnell Fort &amp; chiens de berger</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Fort en pierre millenaire + demonstration de border collies avec moutons (4.9/5 TripAdvisor). Les enfants adorent ! Famille ~28 EUR. Caresser les chiens et agneaux apres le show.<br/><br/><a href="https://caherconnell.com/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g1645258-d1237930-Reviews-Caherconnell_Stone_Fort_Sheepdog_Demonstrations-Caherconnell_The_Burren_County_C.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/guide_voyage_lieu/3409-burren.htm">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Caherconnell+Stone+Fort+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day3</styleUrl>
    <address>Caherconnell Stone Fort, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Poulnabrone Dolmen</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Dolmen de 4200-2900 av. J.-C. au milieu du paysage lunaire du Burren. Acces libre.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186595-d526251-Reviews-Poulnabrone_Dolmen-County_Clare.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/guide_voyage_lieu/3409-burren.htm">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Poulnabrone+Dolmen+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day3</styleUrl>
    <address>Poulnabrone Dolmen, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Cliffs of Moher</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Falaises de 214m sur 8 km. Centre Atlantic Edge. Macareux en aout. Arriver en fin de journee ! Parking officiel : 8 EUR/pers. <strong>Bon plan</strong> : parking fermier 800m avant (direction Liscannor) a 2 EUR/vehicule. Coupe-vent indispensable. Rester dans la zone balisee avec les enfants.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.cliffsofmoher.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g1184916-d214806-Reviews-Cliffs_of_Moher-Liscannor_County_Clare.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/comte-de-clare/falaises-de-moher-cliffs-of-moher">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Cliffs+of+Moher+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day3</styleUrl>
    <address>Cliffs of Moher, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Doolin</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Village mythique de la musique traditionnelle. Pubs legendaires. Enfants bienvenus.<br/><br/><a href="https://doolin.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Tourism-g214506-Doolin_The_Burren_County_Clare-Vacations.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/comte-de-clare/doolin-dulainn">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Doolin+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day3</styleUrl>
    <address>Doolin, County Clare, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J3</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day3</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-9.053,53.2718,0 -9.1253,53.0158,0 -9.14,53.0487,0 -9.4265,52.9719,0 -9.377,53.016,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Doolin</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-9.377,53.016,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J4 — Cote du Clare &amp; retour Galway</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Cascades d&#x27;Ennistymon</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Cascade en plein centre du bourg colore. Arret rapide sur la route.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g212534-d18936468-Reviews-Ennistymon_Falls-Ennistymon_County_Clare.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ennistymon+Falls+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day4</styleUrl>
    <address>Ennistymon Falls, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Lahinch Beach</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Grande plage de sable surveillee en ete. Capitale du surf en Irlande. Parfaite pour les enfants. Aire de jeux juste a cote de la plage. Section baignade surveillee separee du surf. Cours de surf famille possibles des 8 ans.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g212533-d3458853-Reviews-Lahinch_Beach-Lahinch_County_Clare.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/comte-de-clare/lahinch-an-leacht">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lahinch+Beach+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day4</styleUrl>
    <address>Lahinch Beach, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Salthill Promenade</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Front de mer de 2 km. Tradition de « kicker la plaque ». Plongeoir de Blackrock.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186609-d215937-Reviews-Salthill_Promenade-Galway_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/comte-de-galway/salthill">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Salthill+Promenade+Galway+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day4</styleUrl>
    <address>Salthill Promenade, Galway, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Galway Atlantaquaria</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Aquarium national d'Irlande. Bassin tactile (raies, crabes) a hauteur d'enfant. ~1h de visite. <strong>Ideal en plan B pluie</strong> — petit mais les enfants de 5-8 ans adorent les bassins tactiles. Famille ~45 EUR. Ferme le lundi. Dernier acces 16h en semaine.<br/><br/><a href="https://nationalaquarium.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186609-d215896-Reviews-Galway_Atlantaquaria-Galway_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Galway+Atlantaquaria+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day4</styleUrl>
    <address>Galway Atlantaquaria, Salthill, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J4</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day4</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-9.377,53.016,0 -9.29,52.94,0 -9.345,52.937,0 -9.0847,53.258,0 -9.0741,53.2598,0 -9.053,53.2719,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Galway (2e nuit)</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-9.053,53.2719,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J5 — Connemara &amp; Sky Road</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Roundstone</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Village de pecheurs idyllique du Connemara. Atelier de bodhran de Malachy Kearns, l'un des derniers fabricants artisanaux d'Irlande.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/connemara/roundstone-cloch-na-ron">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Roundstone+Connemara+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day5</styleUrl>
    <address>Roundstone, Connemara, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Dog&#x27;s Bay &amp; Gurteen Bay</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Plages jumelles de sable blanc corallien. Eau turquoise. Parmi les plus belles d'Irlande. Tour de la presqu'ile possible en 2h a pied.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g551539-d7106495-Reviews-Dog_s_Bay_Beach-Roundstone_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/connemara/roundstone-cloch-na-ron/dog-s-bay-strand">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Dog's+Bay+Roundstone+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day5</styleUrl>
    <address>Dog's Bay, Roundstone, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Sky Road</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Boucle panoramique de 12 km au-dessus de Clifden. Vues epoustouflantes sur l'ocean et les iles. Privilegier la Upper Sky Road pour les plus belles vues. <strong>Ideal au coucher du soleil</strong> (vers 17-18h). Route etroite, rouler lentement.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g211883-d4442921-Reviews-Sky_Road-Clifden_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/connemara/clifden-an-clochan">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Sky+Road+Clifden+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day5</styleUrl>
    <address>Sky Road, Clifden, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Clifden</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Capitale du Connemara. Rues colorees, bons restaurants, ambiance detendue.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/connemara/clifden-an-clochan">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Clifden+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day5</styleUrl>
    <address>Clifden, Connemara, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J5</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day5</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-9.053,53.2719,0 -9.9203,53.3957,0 -9.9636,53.3779,0 -10.0167,53.4333,0 -10.0965,53.5007,0 -10.0167,53.4333,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Clifden</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-10.0167,53.4333,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J6 — Connemara sauvage &amp; retour Est</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Parc National du Connemara</name>
    <description><![CDATA[3 sentiers : Sruffaunboy (1,5 km, tres facile, platelage bois), Lower Diamond Hill (3 km, faisable des 5-6 ans), Upper (3,8 km, sommet 442m). Gratuit. Demonstrations de chiens de berger en saison.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.connemaranationalpark.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186609-d546269-Reviews-Connemara_National_Park_Visitor_Centre-Galway_County_Galway_Western_Ireland.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/connemara/letterfrack">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Connemara+National+Park+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day6</styleUrl>
    <address>Connemara National Park, Letterfrack, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Viking Tours Athlone</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Croisiere en replique de drakkar viking sur le Shannon (75 min). Les enfants peuvent piloter le bateau ! Casques et epees vikings en vente. Prevoir 75 min.<br/><br/><a href="https://www.vikingtoursireland.ie/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g212091-d1119252-Reviews-Viking_Tours-Athlone_County_Westmeath.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/mag/reportage/a/les-lakelands-l-irlande-secrete">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Viking+Tours+Athlone+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day6</styleUrl>
    <address>Viking Tours, Athlone, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J6</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day6</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-10.0167,53.4333,0 -9.944,53.552,0 -10.0167,53.4333,0 -9.43,53.43,0 -7.9408,53.4232,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Nuit a Athlone</name>
    <styleUrl>#hotel</styleUrl>
    <Point><coordinates>-7.9408,53.4232,0</coordinates></Point>
  </Placemark>
</Folder>
<Folder>
  <name>J7 — Chateaux &amp; colline sacree</name>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Trim Castle</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Plus grand chateau anglo-normand d'Irlande (XIIe). Donjon de 20m, decor de Braveheart. Impressionnant ! Famille 2A+2E ~10 EUR. Visite guidee du donjon 45 min (obligatoire). Brochure en francais. Jardins et enceinte gratuits, belle balade le long de la Boyne.<br/><br/><a href="https://heritageireland.ie/places-to-visit/trim-castle/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g644237-d525404-Reviews-Trim_Castle-Trim_County_Meath.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.routard.com/fr/guide/europe/irlande/environs-de-dublin/trim-castle">Routard</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Trim+Castle+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day7</styleUrl>
    <address>Trim Castle, Trim, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Hill of Tara</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Colline sacree des Hauts Rois d'Irlande. Vue sur 40% de l'ile. Pierre du Destin (Lia Fail). Gratuit (Heritage Card). Centre d'interpretation. Les enfants adorent devaler les collines. 30-45 min suffisent.<br/><br/><a href="https://heritageireland.ie/places-to-visit/hill-of-tara/">Site web</a> | <a href="https://www.tripadvisor.fr/Attraction_Review-g186628-d526324-Reviews-Hill_of_Tara_Temair-County_Meath.html">TripAdvisor</a> | <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hill+of+Tara+Ireland">Google Maps</a>]]></description>
    <styleUrl>#pin-day7</styleUrl>
    <address>Hill of Tara, County Meath, Ireland</address>
  </Placemark>
  <Placemark>
    <name>Route J7</name>
    <styleUrl>#line-day7</styleUrl>
    <LineString>
      <tessellate>1</tessellate>
      <coordinates>-7.9408,53.4232,0 -6.7882,53.5455,0 -6.6113,53.5789,0 -6.2499,53.4264,0</coordinates>
    </LineString>
  </Placemark>
